SUMMARY:Volunteer Work Party at Seattle's Largest Urban Farm
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Rainier Beach Urban Farm & Wetland. \nJoin us the 1st Friday and 3rd Saturday of the month for our wetland work parties at Rainier Beach Urban Farm and Wetlands! We will work together in community to help restore wetland areas of Seattle’s largest urban farm. Support installing native plants\, trail maintenance\, and other stewardship tasks. \nRegister
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/volunteer-work-party-at-seattles-largest-urban-farm/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/volunteer-work-party-at-seattles-largest-urban-farm_97-f6l4fs.jpg
END:VEVENT
