SUMMARY:Leschi Natural Area - Lake Dell Care Giving
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Leschi-Lake Dell Natural Area. \nGive some LOVE to a local favorite! Come help maintain and improve the habitat for all those furry and feathered friends. Join neighbors to create a place for native plants to thrive! \nRegister
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/leschi-natural-area-lake-dell-care-giving/
