SUMMARY:More weeding in Yesler Ravine South
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Yesler Creek Headwaters. \nWeeding in Yesler Ravine North End \nDress for the weather\, sturdy shoes or boots and bring a WATER BOTTLE and a SNACK for our mid-AM break. We’ll have tools and gloves if needed\nIf you have calf high rubber boots wear them – planting will be in the bottom of the ravine and very soggy and wet! \nIf the weather is bad\, check your email around 8AM to see if the work party is cancelled or not. \nRegister
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/more-weeding-in-yesler-ravine-south/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/home-NEW-2-Catherine-Anstett-Trolls-Knoll-gloves.jpg
END:VEVENT
