SUMMARY:Forest restoration with Schmitz Park Restore
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Schmitz Preserve Park. \nHelp the community group\, Schmitz Park Restore\, remove ivy to make room for native plants that will support birds\, insects and other wildlife 🦅 \nRegister
