SUMMARY:Cheasty Forest at Hanford Steps
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a restoration work party at Cheasty GS: Cheasty Blvd. \nPark along 25th Ave S\, south of Hanford street. Do not leave valuables in the car. The light rail station Mount Baker is a short walk away. We can cut back blackberries and other weeds or dig them out. \nRegister \nLearn more about Cheasty Greenspace here.
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/cheasty-forest-at-hanford-steps-24/
