SUMMARY:Roxhill Bog Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Join us as we celebrate this important achievement! \nThe Roxhill Bog Celebration is happening on Thursday\, February 19\, from 10:30am – 12:00pm at Roxhill Park. The event will feature guest speakers\, guided bog tours\, eco-art activities\, along with coffee and snacks. This free\, family friendly event is open to all ages. \nQuestions? Contact: volunteer@dnda.org
URL:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/event/roxhill-bog-celebration/
LOCATION:Roxhill Park\, 2850 SW Roxbury Street\, Seattle\, WA\, 98126\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.seattleparksfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/screenshot-2026-02-04-at-10.39.42-am.png
